# Environment Configuration

This file should be renamed to `.env.local` and contains environment variables for the application.

## API Configuration
VITE_API_BASE_URL=

## Auth0 Authentication (Frontend)
# Get these from Auth0 Dashboard > Applications > Your App > Settings
VITE_AUTH0_DOMAIN=your-tenant.auth0.com
VITE_AUTH0_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id
# Optional: API audience for access tokens (create in Auth0 Dashboard > APIs)
VITE_AUTH0_AUDIENCE=

# Auth0 (Backend verification) - set this in AI_logic/.env
# Used to verify JWT tokens sent via 'Authorization: Bearer <token>' header
AUTH0_DOMAIN=your-tenant.auth0.com
AUTH0_AUDIENCE=https://your-api-identifier

## Feature Flags
VITE_ENABLE_KATEX=
VITE_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=
VITE_ENABLE_TUTOR_MODE=

## Performance
VITE_MAX_PROBLEM_LENGTH=
VITE_API_TIMEOUT=
